    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔表示政策限制足够</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/fed-chair-powell-says-policy-is-sufficiently-restrictive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，当前的货币政策现在是限制性的，随着时间的推移，其限制性足以使通胀回到目标水平。美联储连续第六次会议维持利率不变。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/fed-chair-powell-says-policy-is-sufficiently-restrictive</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 20:23:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>杰罗姆·鲍威尔的美联储词典不知何故未能包含“鹰派”一词</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-05-01/jerome-powell-is-just-dovish-enough-for-investors-fearing-a-hawkish-pivot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比尔·达德利表示，面对具有挑战性的数据，美联储主席发出了“我们已经做到了”的信息]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-05-01/jerome-powell-is-just-dovish-enough-for-investors-fearing-a-hawkish-pivot</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 20:20:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔平息未来加息担忧，信贷市场风险缓解</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/credit-market-risk-eases-as-powell-quells-future-rate-hike-fears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔（Jerome Powell）保证央行不打算进一步加息，令信贷交易员感到一些安慰，从而将企业违约担忧指标降至较低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/credit-market-risk-eases-as-powell-quells-future-rate-hike-fears</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 20:01:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>鲍威尔称美联储下一步行动不太可能加息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/powell-says-fed-s-next-move-being-a-hike-is-unlikely</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在美联储政策制定联邦公开市场委员会决定将基准联邦基金利率目标区间维持在 5.25% 至5.5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/powell-says-fed-s-next-move-being-a-hike-is-unlikely</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 19:48:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鲍威尔：利率是否达到峰值将取决于数据</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/fed-s-powell-whether-rates-at-peak-will-depend-on-data</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔在新闻发布会上表示，在美联储政策制定联邦公开市场委员会决定将基准联邦基金利率的目标区间保留在5.25%至5.5%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/fed-s-powell-whether-rates-at-peak-will-depend-on-data</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 19:34:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储主席鲍威尔暗示降息不会很快到来</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/fed-chair-powell-signals-rate-cuts-aren-t-coming-soon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示，他不知道美联储何时才能获得足够的信心开始降息。他是在美联储维持利率不变后发表上述言论的。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-01/fed-chair-powell-signals-rate-cuts-aren-t-coming-soon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 19:33:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>维京游轮公司 15 亿美元 IPO 后股价上涨 9%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/cruise-line-viking-s-shares-rise-12-after-1-5-billion-us-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[维京控股有限公司 (Viking Holdings Ltd.) 的股价在这家豪华游轮运营商扩大首次公开募股筹集 15.4 亿美元后的首个交易日上涨 8.8%，这表明美国上市复苏的范围仍在扩大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/cruise-line-viking-s-shares-rise-12-after-1-5-billion-us-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 17:00:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国监管机构讨论最早于八月敲定银行资本规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-regulators-discuss-finalizing-bank-capital-rules-as-soon-as-august</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管一些批评人士呼吁废除该计划，但美联储和其他美国顶级监管机构仍在推进其具有里程碑意义的计划，该计划旨在让大银行持有更多资本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/us-regulators-discuss-finalizing-bank-capital-rules-as-soon-as-august</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 16:20:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储利率言论不像人们担心的那么鹰派，金价上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/gold-xauusd-holds-fall-as-markets-brace-for-hawkish-tone-at-fed-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金价上涨，因为投资者对美联储发出的信号感到安慰，即在对价格涨幅正在降温有足够信心后，美联储仍将转向降低借贷成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-01/gold-xauusd-holds-fall-as-markets-brace-for-hawkish-tone-at-fed-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 01 May 2024 01:39:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储的国债反弹并不像人们担心的那样鹰派：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于杰罗姆·鲍威尔淡化加息的可能性，美联储表示将放慢收缩资产负债表以缓解货币市场的压力，全球最大的债券市场飙升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-30/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 22:37:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
